{
  "stem": "21139.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And so once she wrote to me a postcard that she's waiting for my father to camp, because they transferred my mother from Perpignan to the Drancy.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "That is a camp-- the last camp before Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And she thought that my father would come there, and they probably would be together.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But from what I understand from someone that had some information from France, in a book, that they were-- went to Auschwitz on different days-- dates.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "The correspondence that I had both from my father and mother were taken away from me when I was in Vic-sur-Cere.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I had to leave there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And they buried it in the garden.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They said after the war, I should come and pick it up.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Of course, I never received it anymore.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And that I regret very much, not having those last correspondence.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I have no idea.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And as I said, according to that information that I received, they did not see each other anymore.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He only wanted to know if we are well.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They had to be very careful what they wrote to each other because everything was censored.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So there was nothing of consequence that he could ask, or tell us, or anything.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When that-- in-- when that truck came, and that man my father went-- I can see so clearly in front-- in front of me.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was-- and he waved.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[CRYING] [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they took me out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I went to that Girl Guides camp for a short time.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Saint-Sorlin.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was in-- in the country.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was a very pretty surroundings.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] [PAUSES FOR 11 SECONDS] That was July 15, 1942.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In-- I was from March 1941 to July 1942.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "From-- I-- yes, from-- until July '42, I was in Rivesaltes.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
